          "id": "tldr:2023-10-11:o004",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "HOW DISNEY PACKED BIG EMOTION INTO A LITTLE ROBOT",
          "summary": "A Disney Research team recently presented a brand new robotic character during a keynote address. The robot packs an enormous amount of expression into its child-size body, emoting in a way that makes it seem uniquely alive. It uses a system that leverages reinforcement learning to convert an animator's vision into expressive motions. This article discusses how it was developed and the technology behind it - a video of the robot is available.",
          "url": "https://spectrum.ieee.org/disney-robot?utm_source=tldrnewsletter",
          "reading_time_minutes": 5,
